http://vim.wikia.com/wiki/Keep_your_vimrc_file_clean
move all the language-specific stuff from your .vimrc file into a file named .vim/ftplugin/language.vim
If you like most of what Vim's filetype plugin is doing, but you want to override something specific, you can place your settings in .vim/after/ftplugin/language.vim

http://tedlogan.com/techblog3.html
